# MicroTechCorpo Token – Business Plan

## Project Overview
The MicroTechCorpo Token is a digital utility token designed to support the ecosystem of RecGlobalEco and LuxuryMobility.

## Business Use
The token will be used for:
- investor participation
- service payments
- internal settlements
- rewards for strategic partners
- sustainability credits

## Application in RecGlobalEco
- payment for recycling services
- logistics settlements
- material recovery credits
- mobile recycling factory operations

## Application in LuxuryMobility
- premium transport booking
- VIP membership plans
- business client subscriptions
- loyalty reward system

## Revenue Model
- transaction fees
- subscription services
- token-based memberships
- strategic investment rounds

## Estimated Costs
Development: 20,000–50,000 PLN
Legal & compliance: 15,000 PLN
Platform integration: 10,000 PLN
